text: Çalgi Çengi Ikimiz is a 2017 Turkish film. It was released in Turkey by Pinema on 6 January 2017. It is the second film of the series Çalgı Çengi. ==Plot== Two musicians, Salih and Gürkan, described the adventures of their cousins. ==Cast== *Ahmet Kural - Gürkan *Murat Cemcir - Salih *Rasim Öztekin - Bünyamin *Ayhan Taş - İsmet ==Reception== The film was number-one on its opening weekend in Turkey, with . ==References== ==External links== * * Category:Turkish films Category:2017 films Category:Turkish-language films Category:Turkish sequel films Category:Turkish comedy films
